flowPara.flowSpan: Last week we caught wind of a big shipment of various stolen artifacts coming in from overseas. My buddy in customs would love to bust these guys the legal way, but he just found out his boss is working for these smugglers. Way I see it, we hit them at the transfer to prove ourselves as a new crew, my buddy gets paid for his tip but his nose stays clean, and maybe that leads us to a bigger job down the line. The shipment includes three paintings, and a rare jewel, and some prisoner we probably don't want to mess with.
Our objective is to steal the jewel and two paintings.

flowRoot.flowPara: BONUSES: If you steal both J paintings, gain an extra $2k upon success. The prisoner may be freed and guided out.
• Angry Locksmith with Hit 'n' Run and Yank Wires
• Street Urchin with Hurry and Wing It
• Script Kiddie with Bypass and Hit 'n' Run
• Burglar with Wing It and Yank Wires
UPON SUCCESS: For each character who is not busted, level up both character and skills. Add $2k to the team loot.

Sounds like we made a name for ourselves. I was expecting retaliaion, instead we get more work! Good to see our talents are appreciated. Apparently there's an abandoned warehouse that works as a secure storage for a variety of stolen goods being moved by the competitors of these smugglers. Let's show them what we're made of. Our objective is to steal three paintings.
BONUSES: Any painting beyond the 3 gives $2k. If you steal both J/K paintings, gain an extra $2k each.

Well, fellas, I guess those double-crossing smugglers have the feds in their pockets, too. But when they got us pinched, they made some key mistakes. For one, they put us all in the same jail cell. For another, I still have our team loot. I think at this point our best chance of success is to break out of every door simultaneously. Our objective is to exit out of this place, each to a different exit, then, we go our separate ways and never speak of this fiasco again. God speed.
IF PRISONER WAS FREED IN CH.1: Turns out that prisoner was a retired fed! Get 🔍🔍🔍🔍🔍.
